I APPREHEND this is the genuine nature of Chriſtian Redemption, as propoſed by the Goſpel, which will ſtand the teſt, and bring forth the glorious fruits of

                     RIGHTEOUSNESS, PEACE, and JOY in the HOLY GHOST;
